s=\"heading-style-h1\">Mining, Minerals &amp; Natural Resources</h1></div><p class=\"text-size-medium\">Mining, minerals, and natural resources projects come with complex legal and commercial challenges. Our team supports businesses and landowners with practical advice on land acquisition, mineral rights, planning, and development. By bringing together expertise from across the firm, we help you manage risk and move projects forward with confidence. Whether you are involved in a mining project, mineral exploration, or natural resources development, our team is here to support your success.</p></div><div id=\"w-node-_8b2fa05c-57cd-b490-ced6-6fac2cf871aa-2eeda9b8\" class=\"simple_header_grid-right w-variant-0e24fcd7-a2af-940a-c521-6385f08b3d18\"><div class=\"simple-header_image-wrapper w-variant-0e24fcd7-a2af-940a-c521-6385f08b3d18\"><img loading=\"eager\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b44ab164a8844c96471e18/69a9824e9c19616f9038e243_resized_1920px_under_1MB_v11.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"simple-header_image\"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"divider-horizontal\"></div><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"simple_header-component\"><div class=\"padding-section-xsmall\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_component\"><div data-wf--breadcrumb-original--variant=\"base\" class=\"breadcrumb_component\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_div\"><a href=\"/\" class=\"breadcrumb_link w-inline-block\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_page\">Home</div></a><div class=\"breadcrumb_icon w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M5 13h11.17l-4.88 4.88c-.39.39-.39 1.03 0 1.42s1.02.39 1.41 0l6.59-6.59a.996.996 0 0 0 0-1.41l-6.58-6.6a.996.996 0 1 0-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H5c-.55 0-1 .45-1 1s.45 1 1 1\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"breadcrumb_div\