/h4><p>• Secure planning permissions</p><p>• Navigate land use management issues</p><p>• Address statutory infrastructure agreements and planning obligations</p><p>• Interpret planning permissions</p><p>• Manage planning appeals and enforcement</p><p>• Conduct environmental impact assessments</p><p>• Address biodiversity net gain requirements</p><p>‍</p><p>We work closely with clients to ensure compliance with regulatory requirements and local plan policies.</p><p>‍</p><h4>Related areas</h4><p>• Corporate sale and purchase structures</p><p>• Finance, security and bond documentation</p><p>• Commercial agreements</p><p>• Energy related matters</p><p>‍</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></header><div class=\"section_signposts\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div fs-slider-type=\"cms\" fs-slider-instance=\"fs-4-card-slider\" class=\"fs-4-card-slider_instance\"><h2 data-scroll-speed=\"0.025\" data-scroll=\"\" class=\"heading-style-h2\">Our expertise includes</h2><div element-reveal=\"trigger\" fs-slider-element=\"list-wrapper\" class=\"fs-4-card-slider_list-wrapper w-dyn-list\"><div fs-slider-element=\"list\" role=\"list\" class=\"fs-4-card-slider_list w-dyn-items\"><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-4-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><a element-reveal=\"target\" href=\"/for-businesses/planning\" class=\"service-signpost_link w-inline-block\"><div hover-wipe=\"target\" class=\"signpost_content-reveal\"><div class=\"primary_tag\"><p>For</p><p>Businesses</p></div><h4 class=\"heading-style-h5\">Planning</h4><p>Support with planning applications, appeals, and development agreements.</p></div><div class=\"signpost_content\"><h5 class=\"heading-style-h5\">Planning</h5></div><div class=\"signpost_image-wrapper\"><div class=\"image-overlay-layer\"></div><img src=\"/assets/69a6f5e4c46626d48a91b523_Construction_Scaffold_1920w.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset